                    </div>
                    <span>A delighful new approach to home organization. Very focused on 50 specific areas that can be applied to many other situations. Great for the reader short on time but needing both motivation and an understanding of practical methods of organization for the busy family. Written in a positive and crisp manner...</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Don't waste your money.</div>
